  </pd>
       </plentry>
       <plentry>
  <pt>degradationPreference</pt>
  <pd>带宽受限时，视频编码降级偏好。详见 <xref keyref="DEGRADATION_PREFERENCE" /> 。</pd>
       </plentry>
       <plentry>
  <pt>mirrorMode</pt>
  <pd>
      <dl outputclass="since">
 <dlentry>
